name: Report
label: report
definition: document that provides a structured description of something, prepared on ad hoc, periodic, recurring, regular, or as required basis
explanatoryNote: Reports may refer to specific periods, events, occurrences, or subjects, and may be communicated or presented in oral, electronic, or written form.

name: Request
label: request
definition: event in which some party asks another party for something at some point in time

name: RequestActivity
label: request activity
definition: activity in which some party asks another party for something or to do something

name: ReportingParty
label: reporting party
definition: party providing a report, typically in response to some contractual, legal, regulatory or other business requirement

name: Submitter
label: submitter
definition: party presenting something, such as a regulatory report

name: submits
definition: presents something (a proposal, application, report, or other document) for consideration or review
label: submits

name: hasReportDate
label: has report date
definition: date on which a report was issued

name: hasRequestDate
label: has request date
definition: date on which a request was made

name: hasReportDateTime
label: has report date time
definition: date and time at which a report was issued

name: hasRequestDateTime
label: has request date time
definition: date and time at which a request was made

name: isRequestedOf
definition: indicates the party that is asked for something
label: is requested of

name: reportsOn
definition: indicates a subject matter, observation(s), assessment(s), focus or other topic of a report
label: reports on

name: isSubmittedTo
definition: indicates the party to which something is submitted
label: is submitted to

name: isSubmittedBy
definition: indicates the party that submits something
label: is submitted by

name: isReportedTo
label: is reported to
definition: indicates the party to which something is reported

name: isRequestedBy
label: is requested by
definition: indicates the party that asks for something
